1953;;Street of Shadows;;British;;Richard Vernon;;Cesar Romero, Kay Kendall;;crime;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Street_of_Shadows_(1953_film);;Luigi, the owner of a Soho saloon, is romancing an unhappily married socialite, Barbara Gale. He finds himself accused for the murder of ex-girl friend, Angela, who was found stabbed in his apartment. He evades the police and asks his friend Limpy for help. It turns out Limpy was the real killer of Angela.